stvari, nova kola.

329
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:31,357
Sta zelis jos od mene?.

330
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:34,354
Hocu tebe, Dzon. Hocu tebe.

331
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:37,073
