334
00:43:11,640 --> 00:43:14,393
Sta to tamo pravis?
- sredjujem bocu.

335
00:43:15,840 --> 00:43:20,675
Gde ono idemo?
- na sou Dzordz Dzona.

336
00:43:21,960 --> 00:43:24,190
Zar nismo malopre bili tamo?

337
00:43:26,280 --> 00:43:27,713
ostin.
Tamo ste me pokupili.

338
00:43:29,320 --> 00:43:30,389
Hej Dzoni, jesi li video novu
top listu hitova?

339
00:43:31,320 --> 00:43:32,116
placi, placi, placi
je na 14. mestu,

340
00:43:32,160 --> 00:43:32,990
mislim da je tako.

341
00:43:33,920 --> 00:43:35,638
